{"tid":1838312,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【名後面乜都冇】英籍胡杏兒任春晚主持 被網民質疑避寫國籍","createTime":"2020-01-24T03:35:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T08:01:46.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"79eb2cbde1b0ef514025c308d6431b4cafc7f5d0","tid":1838312,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:35:45.000Z","msg":"湖北武漢爆發新冠狀病毒肺炎疫情，為控制疫情蔓延，就連一年一度的央視春晚，亦全部取消直播部份，改為提早錄影。<br />\n<br />\n早前被指踏上央視春晚位於珠海「粵港澳大灣區」舞台的胡杏兒，今次在春晚中擔任主持，與表演嘉賓劉嘉玲、成龍等同台。不過在春晚的節目表中，有大陸網民就質疑當劉嘉玲、成龍，就算是已入籍香港的郎朗，人名後均有顯示是其國籍是「中國香港」時，為何胡杏兒卻沒有，更懷疑她是否因早已移民英國而避寫。<br />\n<br />\n而除此之外，有網民亦指今年的春晚做演員的胡杏兒被派去做主持、劉嘉玲則被安排唱歌，至於彭于晏就與甄澤權表演魔術，覺得節目安排非常奇怪。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200123/large/1579787700_8e3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200123%2Flarge%2F1579787700_8e3e.jpg&h=274261a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200123/large/1579787700_faca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200123%2Flarge%2F1579787700_faca.jpg&h=f279787c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200123/large/1579787700_5315.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200123%2Flarge%2F1579787700_5315.jpg&h=230c01e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200123/L5OM4VTHLXYD347Q7TYDJQJSTI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200123%2FL5OM4VTHLXYD347Q7TYDJQJSTI%2F&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JXzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=c16c698a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200123%2FL5OM4VTHLXYD347Q7TYDJQJSTI%2F&h=32ba4936\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200123/L5OM4VTHLXYD347Q7TYDJQJSTI/</a>"},{"pid":"6a3f62ec0ed1112ecd03c24553b7986e26f2764e","tid":1838312,"uid":61281,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:39:54.000Z","msg":"Soler奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"036547acdd596e0d43430976274bbf086c2b0db2","tid":1838312,"uid":32716,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:39:56.000Z","msg":"要寫國籍本身就on9啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4fb6ccb32319a80dc9c2539e539b91552bc8c24","tid":1838312,"uid":152925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6a3f62ec0ed1112ecd03c24553b7986e26f2764e","tid":1838312,"uid":61281,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:39:54.000Z","msg":"Soler奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:55:43.000Z","msg":"奶左好耐啦"},{"pid":"6eb5b222cb37420a38e22fccaa049cac657952e4","tid":1838312,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"036547acdd596e0d43430976274bbf086c2b0db2","tid":1838312,"uid":32716,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:39:56.000Z","msg":"要寫國籍本身就on9啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T08:01:46.000Z","msg":"雜種屋企人寫哂英美國藉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}